# Walkthrough - Fix missing `updateFile` in [useFileManager](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/CustomFilePicker.tsx#145-218)

I have added the `updateFile` method to the [useFileManager](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/CustomFilePicker.tsx#145-218) hook in [CustomFilePicker.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/CustomFilePicker.tsx). This resolves the TypeScript error in [CreatePost.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/pages/CreatePost.tsx) and enables functionality like image cropping to update the file manager's state.

## Changes Made

### [CustomFilePicker](file:///c:/Users/elink/./gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/CustomFilePicker.tsx)

#### [MODIFY] [CustomFilePicker.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/./gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/CustomFilePicker.tsx)

- Implemented `updateFile` using `useCallback`:
    ```tsx
    const updateFile = useCallback((id: string, updates: Partial<FileItem>) => {
      setFiles((prev) =>
        prev.map((f) => {
          if (f.id === id) {
            if (updates.url && updates.url !== f.url) {
              URL.revokeObjectURL(f.url);
            }
            return { ...f, ...updates };
          }
          return f;
        })
      );
    }, []);
    ```
- Included `updateFile` in the `useMemo` return object of the hook.

## Verification Results

### Manual Verification
- Verified that [CreatePost.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/pages/CreatePost.tsx) now correctly references `updateFile` on the `fileManager` object.
- The `updateFile` implementation correctly handles merging updates and revoking old `URL` objects to prevent memory leaks during repeated edits/crops.
- All other components using [useFileManager](file:///c:/Users/elink/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/CustomFilePicker.tsx#145-218) now have access to this utility method if needed.

